---
title: Login Flow (JWT Authentication)
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant FE as React Frontend
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant AUTH as Auth Service
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: Enter email + password
    FE->>GW: POST /auth/login
    GW->>AUTH: Forward login request
    AUTH->>DB: Query user by email
    DB-->>AUTH: User data (hashed password)
    AUTH->>AUTH: Verify BCrypt hash

    alt Credentials valid
        AUTH->>AUTH: Generate JWT (claims)
        AUTH-->>GW: 200 OK + JWT
        GW-->>FE: 200 OK + JWT
        FE->>FE: Store JWT (state / storage)
        FE-->>U: Redirect to dashboard
    else Credentials invalid
        AUTH-->>GW: 401 Unauthorized
        GW-->>FE: 401 Unauthorized
        FE-->>U: Display "Invalid credentials"
    end
